itunes:summary:
Ross Patterson and Dan Hollaway are joined by special guest Hamody "The Terrorist Whisperer" Jasim as he breaks down new intel of how Iran is beating the US in sanctions against the country by illegally funneling in money through Iraq.  He also gives exclusive details of the the three banks that are laundering the money and how the Kurds are involved.
